<p>Doing little studies like this can really take the pressure off from the bigger or more important pieces. These are about 5 inch tall and I try..&rsquo;try&rsquo; to not spend too long on each. I&rsquo;d recommend working small and moving on quickly if you&rsquo;re trying to build a daily habit.</p>
